This project creates a safe and empathetic chatbot using Natural Language Processing (NLP) to provide non-clinical emotional support. It is built to simulate friendly dialogue, offering users a comforting space to express their feelings.

## âœ… Objective

The goal of this project is to develop a chatbot that offers general mental health support without giving clinical advice. It responds in a supportive tone and avoids any conversation around crisis or diagnoses.

